reviews.text: Good well stocked cinema hall. Decent sound system. Well trained staff. The arcade mall seems empty though.

A favourite for the neighbourhood or even that district as not many cinemas around.  Provides current movies but normally not full as it is away from the most crowded residential areas.  Tickets are normally cheaper than those in the busy districts.  Deco & sound system also ok and located in an extremely spacious and quiet mall
Good deal for movie goers.cheaper movie ticket compare to the downtown area.
One of the best cinemas in Hong Kong simply because it’s far away from the crowds so usually less people. If you liked to enjoy movies quietly then this is your place.
